== ShareAcl v0.3 ==

New features:
- Added AccountView page to show all accounts and their associated folders and ACEs.

Improvements:
- Added indexing to the database schema for efficient lookup of ACEs by trustee and folder.
- Added indexing to the database schema for efficient lookup of ACEs by rights mask and access control type.

Bug fixes:
- Fixed issue with group membership resolution in Invoke-ShareAclResolver.ps1 to include primary group members and de-duplicate results by SID.